		{"id":"9a513b6d2b61e09a","type":"text","text":"# Ragno Start Interaction\n\ntodo: Ragno sits across from the player. They're looking to discuss the school and other characters.\n\nnext:","x":-9679,"y":2965,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"e7a724a9b93a5575","type":"text","text":"# Mystic Start Interaction\n\ntodo: Mystic sits next to the player. They're looking to discuss the school and other characters.\n\nnext:","x":-9679,"y":3261,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"1b6eb8e72b63c9e6","type":"text","text":"# Mystic Judges Food\n\ntodo: Mystic judges the player based on their choice of food.\n\nnext:","x":-9241,"y":3261,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"47761752e594cd0d","type":"text","text":"# Mystic End Interaction\n\ntodo: Closing remarks from Mystic as they leave the cafeteria. The player follows out to the courtyard of the school.\n\nnext:","x":-8821,"y":3261,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"a65c7565dde2e814","type":"text","text":"# NPC Joins Table\n\ntodo: A random student NPC who is NOT the one the player sat next to in class joins the player at their lunch table.\n\nnext:","x":-10202,"y":2858,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"6683a0b668eb4d0b","type":"text","text":"# Chose Food\n\ntodo: This would be multiple blocks depending on the food the player selects. \n\nnext:","x":-10202,"y":2595,"width":380,"height":219,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"70c4d4d1ef6fcf62","type":"text","text":"# Mystic Interrupts Ragno\n\ntodo: Mystic interrupts the player's interaction with Ragno. The player can choose to either stand up and fight back or forfeit their money to Mystic. Ragno judges the player accordingly.\n\nnext:","x":-8821,"y":2965,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"4c4dc4d67406d617","type":"text","text":"# Ragno End Interaction\n\ntodo: Closing remarks from Ragno as they leave the cafeteria. The player follows out to the courtyard of the school.\n\nnext:","x":-8401,"y":2965,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"ca196923196d120d","type":"text","text":"# Mystic Interrupts Primal\n\ntodo: Mystic interrupts the player's interaction with Primal. The player can choose to either stand up and fight back or forfeit their money to Mystic. Primal judges the player accordingly.\n\nnext:","x":-8821,"y":2665,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
