		{"id":"751860c26a1b82f9","type":"text","text":"# Get Food\n\ntodo: The player decides to get food. They choose which kind.\n\nnext:","x":-10202,"y":2076,"width":380,"height":220,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"3f461570915dc006","type":"text","text":"# Femchro Start Interaction\n\ntodo: Femchro sits in the seat right next to the player. They maintain their uppity-attitude.\n\nnext:","x":-9679,"y":2365,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"87da21457283789c","type":"text","text":"# Don't Get Food\n\ntodo: The player is hungry. But they sit it out.\n\nnext:","x":-10202,"y":2365,"width":380,"height":200,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"5daf2cfd1fdc8f61","type":"text","text":"# Lead Start Interaction\n\ntodo: Lead joins the player at the table. They speak in a typical lead way.\n\nnext:","x":-9679,"y":2066,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"3a7c190d0ae32d97","type":"text","text":"# Absolutely!\n\nflag: sat_with_creeper = true\n\ntext: \"As you take your seat across from the professor you feel your stomach overcome with butterflies. What a strange feeling...\"\n\nnext:","x":-9740,"y":-6514,"width":680,"height":280,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"fea361ea71662c7b","type":"text","text":"# I love data packing!\n\ntext: ragno(disappointed): \"So many people like packing data.\"\n\ntext: ragno(idle): \"Do you have what it takes to stand out?\"\n\ntext: \"In the middle of speaking Ragno is interrupted by Professor Magnet addressing the class.\"\n\nnext:\n\n","x":-11730,"y":-4383,"width":460,"height":320,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"c0eacecc16dc3ded","type":"text","text":"# I've got to get to class!\n\nflag: creeper_upset = true\n\ntext: \"You ignore the fallen fellow and continue on your way. While you attempt to jump over them though your foot lands on one of their papers. You slip, but manage to catch yourself and continue your sprint.\"\n\nbackground: classroom(fade)\n\ntext: \"You arrive at the class, only to find that there is no professor! As you gawk at the room the door behind you creaks open and Dr. Magnet walks in. With each step the click of his shoes against the floor echoes through the silent classroom.\"\n\nenter: creeper\n\ntext: creeper: \"Good morning, class.\"\n\ntext: \"Dr. Magnet walks to his desk and sits down, shooting a horrifyingly mean glare at you!\"\n\nnext:","x":-11260,"y":-6540,"width":680,"height":540,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"0dc01521211c6346","type":"text","text":"# Ragno || Uses trap\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-12286,"y":2192,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"7aa7e99a8755d739","type":"text","text":"# Hunts With Ragno\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-12739,"y":2192,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"7ae689409a42cf16","type":"text","text":"# Primal || Accident\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-11828,"y":1160,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"04d0c453682ca426","type":"text","text":"# Ragno || Slacks Off\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-12286,"y":2484,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"a47669c677c9e3da","type":"text","text":"# Ragno || Accident\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-11828,"y":2050,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"54ea9196f7ba1354","type":"text","text":"# Ragno || Success\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-11828,"y":2350,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"f86468bd3986807e","type":"text","text":"# Hunts With Primal\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-12739,"y":1312,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"ef40db81a22f5117","type":"text","text":"# Professor Magnet is my idol!\n\ntext: ragno(flustered): \"Aww. That's cute. He was my idol once too.\"\n\ntext: \"In the middle of speaking Ragno is interrupted by Professor Magnet addressing the class.\"\n\nnext:","x":-11730,"y":-3983,"width":460,"height":260,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"037267497e13c5e2","type":"text","text":"# It's a long story!\n\ntext: ragno(idle): \"I'm sure we have a little while to talk—\"\n\ntext: \"In the middle of her sentence Professor Magnet interrupts the entire class.\"\n\nnext:","x":-11730,"y":-3643,"width":460,"height":260,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"e5c473e63a1513c7","type":"text","text":"# Well, apparently Professor Magnet personally chose me.\n\ntext: ragno(disappointed): \"Ouch. It hurts to learn you didn't earn your keep.\"\n\ntext: ragno(flustered): \"Interesting to know Creeper—sorry, Professor Magnet—thinks your promising enough to have hand-picked you from his roster, though.\"\n\ntext: \"In the middle of her sentence Professor Magnet interrupts the entire class.\"\n\nnext:","x":-11730,"y":-3303,"width":460,"height":400,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"b4b2ac5fcdccc366","type":"text","text":"# Ragno || Hunts on Foot\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-12286,"y":1892,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"4d580726c303fe58","type":"text","text":"# Primal || Slacks Off\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-12286,"y":1604,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"d3dba43074617bab","type":"text","text":"# Primal || Success\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-11828,"y":1460,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"85bb5ec445d84f56","type":"text","text":"# Primal || Uses trap\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-12286,"y":1312,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"b3c79b3e11d8a4ce","type":"text","text":"# Creeper || Hunts on Foot\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-12286,"y":2920,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"15d41d729d648bec","type":"text","text":"# Creeper || Accident\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-11828,"y":2920,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"b587445a7eda944e","type":"text","text":"# Creeper || Uses trap\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-12286,"y":3220,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"5052cd953c47812e","type":"text","text":"# Creeper || Success\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-11828,"y":3220,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"b111495947428413","type":"text","text":"# Hunts With Creeper\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-12739,"y":3072,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"31f0a6ce0958be43","type":"text","text":"# Turn in Hunt\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-10671,"y":981,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"64c9730c586f094d","type":"text","text":"# Return from Hunt\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-11091,"y":822,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"4c485844da93636c","type":"text","text":"# Argue Immorality\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-10671,"y":652,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"b3b0bd0db5ac4926","type":"text","text":"# The Bus\n\ntodo: Second bus trip, on the way back to the school. Player can once again pick who they want to sit with.\n\nnext:","x":-10171,"y":812,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"5d2346993075f3c9","type":"text","text":"# Sits With Lead\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-9731,"y":130,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"4225c29e60dc11f7","type":"text","text":"# Uhm.\n\ntext: femchro(disappointed): \"Sorry, I don't mean to be so boisterous...\"\n\ntext: femchro(idle): \"I'm just excited!\"\n\ntext: femchro(idle): \"So, why did you choose Creeper's College?\"\n\nchoice: \\[\n\"I love data packing!\",\n\"Professor Magnet is my idol!\",\n\"It's a long story!\",\n{if: learned_was_picked = true: \"Well, apparently Professor Magnet personally chose me.\"}\n]","x":-14080,"y":-3411,"width":460,"height":440,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"6c33dec1073cc66e","type":"text","text":"# Yeah, I'm ok!\n\ntext: creeper(idle): \"Well, that's good to hear! Was quite the crash we had back there.\"\n\ntext: creeper(flushed): \"Say, we're both headed to the same place, right? Why don't you follow me to the classroom.\"\n\ncharacter: creeper(idle)\n\nnext:","x":-10500,"y":-7214,"width":680,"height":280,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"bc687adeac42ae3d","type":"text","text":"# I- Um- I- Uh-\n\ntext: creeper(disappointed): \"You really took quite the tumble there, didn't you... Let's get to the classroom so you can sit down.\"\n\nbackground: classroom(fade)\n\ntext: creeper(idle): \"You can go ahead and sit in the front if you would like.\"\n\nchoice: \"Would you like to sit with Dr. Magnet?\"","x":-10500,"y":-6854,"width":680,"height":280,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"ff040da1f256cdca","type":"text","text":"# Enter the classroom with Dr. Magnet\n\nbackground: classroom(fade)\n\ntext: \"The two of you enter the classroom together. Everyone is already seated throughout the room and you appear to be the last two to enter.\"\n\ntext: creeper: \"Please, take a seat [player_name].\"\n\ntext: \"Dr. Magnet walks over to his desk and takes a seat, waiting for you to sit down.\"\n\nnext:","x":-9740,"y":-7214,"width":680,"height":320,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"9a13713d67f0ee25","type":"text","text":"# I think I'll sit somewhere else...\n\ntext: creeper(disappointed): \"Oh. I understand.\"\n\ntext: \"You walk away, Dr. Magnet seems disappointed but you hope your decision was for the best...\"\n\nnext:","x":-9740,"y":-6814,"width":680,"height":220,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"5b645354886f5861","type":"text","text":"# Chose Femchro\n\nenter: femchro\n\nvar: seat = 1\n\ntext: \"You take a seat next to Femchro. She seems high-energy, but in a good way! The room is full of noise as students chatter amongst each other.\"\n\ntext: femchro(idle): \"Oh-em-gee! You're [player_name] right? You seem pretty cool! I didn't think anyone was going to sit here so I'm a little surprised~!\"\n\nchoice:","x":-14629,"y":-3385,"width":460,"height":387,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"93a5895332b62093","type":"text","text":"# These seats looked comfortable!\n\ntext: femchro(flustered): \"They are so comfy!\"\n\ntext: femchro(disappointed): \"No one ever sits with me, and I always pick the best seats!\"\n\ntext: femchro(idle): \"But you did!\"\n\ntext: femchro: \"So, what brought you to Creeper's College!?\"\n\nchoice: \\[\n\"I love data packing!\",\n\"Professor Magnet is my idol!\",\n\"It's a long story!\",\n{if: learned_was_picked = true: \"Well, apparently Professor Magnet personally chose me.\"}\n]\n","x":-14080,"y":-2891,"width":460,"height":520,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"d27b95b75c0bc3eb","type":"text","text":"# It's a long story!\n\ntext: femchro(flustered): \"Ooo! You can tell me all about it later!\"\n\ntext: \"In the middle of her sentence Professor Magnet interrupts the entire class.\"\n\nnext:","x":-13549,"y":-3112,"width":460,"height":269,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"e13729ee563e577c","type":"text","text":"# Well, apparently Professor Magnet personally chose me.\n\ntext: femchro(flustered): \"That must mean he likes you!\"\n\ntext: femchro(idle): \"Professor Magnet is super strict and selective, so to have been hand-picked must mean there's something special about you!\"\n\ntext: \"In the middle of her sentence Professor Magnet interrupts the entire class.\"\n\nnext:","x":-13549,"y":-2772,"width":460,"height":369,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"d2155c967547bcc1","type":"text","text":"# Hi!\n\ntext: ragno(surprised): \"Oh! Didn't notice you there. Hi.\"\n\ntext: ragno(flushed): \"Sorry. I'm not used to being in public spaces like this.'\"\n\ntext: ragno(idle): \"What brings you to this class?\"\n\nchoice: \\[\n\"I love data packing!\",\n\"Professor Magnet is my idol!\",\n\"It's a long story!\",\n{if: learned_was_picked = true: \"Well, apparently Professor Magnet personally chose me.\"}\n]","x":-12269,"y":-3383,"width":460,"height":420,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"77d139f934375771","type":"text","text":"# ... Hey.\n\ntext: ragno(surprised): \"Oh! Didn't notice you there. Hi.\"\n\ntext: ragno(disappointed): \"Hope I didn't scare you off with that. I'm not used to being in public spaces with so much noise. It's strange.\"\n\ntext: ragno(idle): \"What brings you to this class?\"\n\nchoice: \\[\n\"I love data packing!\",\n\"Professor Magnet is my idol!\",\n\"It's a long story!\",\n{if: learned_was_picked = true: \"Well, apparently Professor Magnet personally chose me.\"}\n]","x":-12269,"y":-4343,"width":460,"height":440,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"53488c300193deae","type":"text","text":"# Rush back, I need my food!\n\nbackground: player_bedroom(fade)\n\ntext: \"You rush back to your dorm, grabbing your lunch box before rushing back to the school.\"\n\nbackground: schoolyard(fade)\n\ntext: \"As you arrive at the schoolyard you find it desolate, besides one person who you mistakenly run into in your rush. You both crash to the ground.\"\n\nsound: crash\n\ntext: unknown: \"My apologies...\"\n\ntext: \"As you both get back up from the ground you lock eyes, it's your professor!\"\n\nenter: creeper\n\ntext: creeper: \"Sorry about that... Say, you look familiar? You're [player_name] aren't you? I remember picking you out from all the other students! I'm sorry we had to meet like this!\"\n\ntext: \"You're stunned that Dr. Magnet would even recognize you, let alone have selectively picked you from the other students!\"\n\ntext: creeper(shocked): \"Are... Are you ok? You're a little red...\"\n\nchoice:","x":-12040,"y":-7214,"width":706,"height":674,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"7f33d62993305a60","type":"text","text":"# I'll survive. School lunch can't be that bad?\n\nflag: forgot_lunchbox = true\n\ntext: \"Despite forgetting your food you continue to run to your classroom, but on the way there you accidentally run into another hustler! You both collapse to the ground with a thud, spilling their belongings across the sidewalk! They begin to frantically pick them up.\"\n\nsound: crash\n\nchoice: \"What are you to do!\"","x":-12040,"y":-6460,"width":706,"height":300,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"37a149fc1a633ac1","type":"text","text":"# Hi?\n\ntext: ragno(surprised): \"Oh! Didn't notice you there. Hi.\"\n\ntext: ragno(idle): \"So, what brings you to this class?\"\n\nchoice: \\[\n\"I love data packing!\",\n\"Professor Magnet is my idol!\",\n\"It's a long story!\",\n{if: learned_was_picked = true: \"Well, apparently Professor Magnet personally chose me.\"}\n]","x":-12269,"y":-3823,"width":460,"height":360,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"88208df003c06278","type":"text","text":"# Help them!\n\ntext: \"You crouch down and begin to help them recollect their belongings, apologizing for the upheaval.\"\n\nflag: creeper_upset = false\n\ntext: unknown: \"No worries. Thanks for the help!\"\n\ntext: \"As you both stand up you lock gaze, realizing who you have just bumped into your body locks up.\"\n\nenter: creeper\n\nflag: learned_was_picked = true\n\nsound: sparkles\n\ntext: creeper: \"Say, you look familiar? You're [player_name] aren't you? I remember picking you out from all the other students!\"\n\ntext: creeper(shocked): \"I'm sorry we had to meet like this! Are... Are you ok? You're looking a little stiff!\"\n\nchoice:","x":-11260,"y":-7214,"width":680,"height":594,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"2029f9fdd96e05a8","type":"text","text":"# Go back to bed.\n\ntext: \"You gently push one of the your hands from out beneath the comforter and turn off the alarm before drifting back into unconsciousness.\"\n\nend:","x":-12720,"y":-7214,"width":596,"height":200,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"592a2b22f3692750","type":"text","text":"# Just a little bit longer...\n\ntext: \"Just as you feel like you're dozing back off the alarm sounds off again! That darn alarm!\"\n\ntext: \"Your bed is warm and cozy, comforting like a mother's womb. Your eyelids feel like anvils, the comforter like a loving hug. The room is dark and of a nice temperature. Alexa massages your eardrums with whale calls and white-noise. It is an environment well-suited to a little more rest.\"\n\nchoice: \"What are you to do in this situation but remain entranced by such heavenly feelings? To disturb such peaceful rest would be unjust and frankly even illegal.\"","x":-13400,"y":-7214,"width":600,"height":360,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"8caa115718942b83","type":"text","text":"# Wake up!\n\ntext: \"You get out of bed and begin your morning routine. Shower taken, hair combed, teeth brushed, and body dressed. You are ready for the day ahead! You grab and neatly organize the items in your backpack, carefully remembering everything you need to grab before heading off to school.\"\n\nbackground: schoolyard(fade)\n\ntext: \"You arrive to the bustling courtyard just as the bell rings. Students begin flocking to their lectures and dorms, scurrying like insects who have witnessed the hands of a benevolent God dislodging the rock which they sit beneath.\"\n\ntext: \"You too begin the trek to your own classroom, arriving just in time to be welcomed by your professor.\"\n\nbackground: classroom(fade)\n\nenter: creeper\n\ntext: \"You are surprised to see that Dr. Magnet will be your professor! You always looked up to him as a child, and to be accepted onto his very own campus and now attend his lectures! It was a dream come true!\"\n\nnext:","x":-13400,"y":-6769,"width":600,"height":640,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"11bad5b2ed26721a","type":"text","text":"# Chose Ragno\n\nenter: ragno\n\nvar: seat = 3\n\ntext: \"You take a seat next to Ragno. She seems disinterested in the class itself, intently watching the others in the room instead. The room is full of noise as students chatter amongst each other. Amongst the noise she completely misses you sitting down next to her.\"\n\nchoice:","x":-12809,"y":-3833,"width":460,"height":380,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"4f6fc21c921f7570","type":"text","text":"# I love data packing!\n\ntext: femchro(flustered): \"Who doesn't!?\"\n\ntext: femchro(idle): \"If we didn't like it why would we have applied for the school!\"\n\ntext: \"In the middle of speaking Femchro is interrupted by Professor Magnet addressing the class.\"\n\nnext:\n\n","x":-13549,"y":-3843,"width":460,"height":308,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"80818e9ec865f7af","type":"text","text":"# Professor Magnet is my idol!\n\ntext: femchro(flustered): \"Mine too!\"\n\ntext: femchro(idle): \"We have so much in common!\"\n\ntext: \"In the middle of speaking Femchro is interrupted by Professor Magnet addressing the class.\"\n\nnext:","x":-13549,"y":-3463,"width":460,"height":271,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"b4cee3f75153959f","type":"text","text":"# Name Confirmed\n\ntext: \"You feel something grab you, pulling you upwards into what you can only assume is the sky. Your eyes shoot wide open as  a blinding light consumes your sight.\"\n\nsound: alarm_clock\n\nchoice: \"You wake up to the sound of your alarm clock, reminding you that today is your first day at your new college! But your eyes are so heavy...\"","x":-13840,"y":-7194,"width":384,"height":354,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"25b33e0eab45c4a0","type":"text","text":"# Jump from bed, I need to get ready!\n\ntext: \"Despite the universes best efforts to keep you asleep you jump from your covers and begin preparing for the day ahead!\"\n\ntext: \"Bathed, combed, brushed, and dressed, you quickly hovel together your belongings, shoving them into your backpack before heading out your door.\"\n\nbackground: schoolyard(fade)\n\nchoice: \"By the time you exit your dorm you realize you've forgotten your lunch box!\"","x":-12720,"y":-6934,"width":596,"height":356,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"f387d720fb07c117","type":"text","text":"# Femchro\n\nenter: femchro\n\ntext: femchro: \"Hiya!!! My name's Femchro! I *LOVE* making data packs! Though my specialty is in the arts, I dabble in the practical too!...\"\n\ntext: femchro(flustered): \"Some people like to say I'm 'quirky', but personally I like to think of myself as out-going! I'm really looking forward to meeting all of you this semester! Best of luck in your classes!\"\n\ncharacter: femchro(idle)\n\nnext:","x":-14400,"y":-5743,"width":460,"height":420,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"3a9b905628261cf3","type":"text","text":"# Lead\n\nenter: lead\n\ntext: lead: \"...\"\n\ntext: lead(flustered): \"...\"\n\ncharacter: lead(idle)\n\nnext:","x":-14400,"y":-5243,"width":460,"height":300,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"5a7cff4499bffe37","type":"text","text":"# Ragno\n\nenter: ragno\n\ntext: ragno: \"Hey! My name's Ragno. I used to make data packs, but really I'm taking this class to get credits for the degree I actually want.\"\n\ncharacter: ragno(idle)\n\nnext:","x":-14400,"y":-4863,"width":460,"height":300,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"5a4317abb34ff9a1","type":"text","text":"# Oh, thanks!\n\ntext: femchro(flustered): \"No problem! You're a little cute, too~!\"\n\ntext: femchro(idle): \"So, why The Creeper's College!?\"\n\nchoice: \\[\n\"I love data packing!\",\n\"Professor Magnet is my idol!\",\n\"It's a long story!\",\n{if: learned_was_picked = true: \"Well, apparently Professor Magnet personally chose me.\"}\n]","x":-14080,"y":-3871,"width":460,"height":380,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"6b3f390cfde3eb7a","type":"text","text":"# Name Input\n\nreminder: Put name input section here\n\nnext:","x":-14180,"y":-7124,"width":260,"height":180,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"3bbc8eaee8e59990","type":"text","text":"# Start\n\nbackground: darkness\n\ntext: \"You are swallowed into the abyss. Darkness of the deepest and most conceptual form surrounds you.\"\n\ntext: \"You feel nothing. You see nothing. You are... nothing. Or... you were? What are you? *Who are you?*\"\n\nnext:","x":-14700,"y":-7214,"width":420,"height":360,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"7dfa9c9e39901eda","type":"text","text":"# Meet class\n\ntext: creeper(idle): \"Hello everyone. I am Dr. Magnet, namesake of the college which you are currently attending, and henceforth your homeroom instructor. I would like to formally welcome you all...\"\n\ntext: creeper(flustered): \"To The Creeper's College.\"\n\ntext: creeper(idle): \"Could I have everyone who is currently seated stand up! Since everyone here is new to the school let's take a moment to introduce ourselves.\"\n\nexit: creeper\n\ntext: \"Amidst everyone standing up and introducing themselves only a select few other students catch your eye... or ear?\"\n\nnext:","x":-15020,"y":-5743,"width":540,"height":460,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"0dd624088c461056","type":"text","text":"# Primal || Hunts on Foot\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-12286,"y":1012,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"d3e39131ab6b0186","type":"text","text":"# Flux || Slacks Off\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-13727,"y":2462,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"3d2eae8369a7ef3e","type":"text","text":"# Femchro || Hunts on Foot\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-13727,"y":2750,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"b7c5924cb1ac9817","type":"text","text":"# Femchro || Accident\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-13267,"y":2902,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"ba573de87cc8db07","type":"text","text":"# Femchro || Uses trap\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-13727,"y":3050,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"8f38f6dc8e219572","type":"text","text":"# Femchro || Success\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-13267,"y":3202,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"b2fc2c6fb4eedcd0","type":"text","text":"# Lead || Uses trap\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-13727,"y":1290,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"3718947947fb738b","type":"text","text":"# Lead || Slacks Off\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-13727,"y":1582,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"d266793ee4f09f3f","type":"text","text":"# Lead || Success\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-13267,"y":1442,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"f89b42494cfbef68","type":"text","text":"# Flux || Uses trap\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-13727,"y":2170,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"97cbbd87077691cc","type":"text","text":"# Flux || Accident\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-13267,"y":2170,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"97a69ffd19d63120","type":"text","text":"# Flux || Hunts on Foot\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-13727,"y":1870,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"9a82ef1ee985ff1d","type":"text","text":"# Lead || Hunts on Foot\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-13727,"y":990,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"d1814db446e320af","type":"text","text":"# Lead || Accident\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-13267,"y":1142,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"3e6bf29d5fddc208","type":"text","text":"# Hunts With Lead\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-14195,"y":1290,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"7fbe8346fcab38ef","type":"text","text":"# Hunts With Flux\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-14195,"y":2170,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"b20ff45c52f2a93f","type":"text","text":"# Sits With Lead\n\ntodo: The player sits next to Lead on the bus. There is some form of commentary on the player not feeling too well, like they're car sick. They must overcome the challenge of not puking on the bus ride.\n\nnext:","x":-15455,"y":869,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"85a1610b2fd689aa","type":"text","text":"# Sits With Flux\n\ntodo: The player sits next to Flux on the bus. They have a little bit of banter, but ultimately not much.\n\nnext:","x":-15455,"y":1168,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"073894192b6d1884","type":"text","text":"# Sits With Femchro\n\ntodo: The player sits with Femchro on the bus. They chat about their favorite movie! Femchro is a bit of a movie nerd.\n\nnext:","x":-15455,"y":1457,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"35ee2ff5d1f93075","type":"text","text":"# Arrive in Swamp\n\ntodo: The bus arrives and everyone unloads. Creeper addresses the class and lets them know how things will go down. People are lined up and allowed to pick who they want to team up with. The player is allowed to pick from any of their classmates, they may choose Creeper if they scored high enough in yesterday's test. Creeper gives them this option as an award.\n\nnext:","x":-14975,"y":1587,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"5ba30a07c67d84ed","type":"text","text":"# Sits Alone\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-15455,"y":2657,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"dbb7f90c1d21d3e9","type":"text","text":"# Sits With Primal\n\ntodo: The player sits with Primal on the bus. They discuss\n\nnext:","x":-15455,"y":1757,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"11414e1af0420a8a","type":"text","text":"# Sits With Ragno\n\ntodo: The player sits with Ragno on the bus. She tries to convince them that she's a good choice to go hunting with.\n\nnext:","x":-15455,"y":2057,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"ff92d6f61a25bffb","type":"text","text":"# Sits With Creeper\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-15455,"y":2360,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"a9fdf5ccdca6d6ca","type":"text","text":"# Hunts With Femchro\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-14195,"y":3050,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"a216f5814a8e50c7","type":"text","text":"# Femchro || Slacks Off\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-13727,"y":3342,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"3b31ba879ed72cbb","type":"text","text":"# The Bus\n\ntodo: The class loads onto the bus. The player chooses who to sit next to.\n\nnext:","x":-15895,"y":1357,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"89dc61c28f7c518e","type":"text","text":"# Creeper\n\ntodo: Magnet is addressing the students, letting them know what will be happening during the day.\n\nnext:","x":-16315,"y":1357,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"fe006a0d3d9383be","type":"text","text":"# Tuesday Start\n\ntodo: The player wakes up and can sleep in, but ONLY if they didn't sleep in on the first day.\n\nnext:","x":-17695,"y":1327,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"ce004fd7fa30d0a8","type":"text","text":"# Slept In\n\ntodo: The player can forget their lunch again, like in the first day.\n\nnext:","x":-17255,"y":1197,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"cfcd3ade762c3da8","type":"text","text":"# Didn't Sleep In\n\ntodo: The player makes it to school on-time with their lunch in-hand.\n\nnext:","x":-17255,"y":1517,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"1f77a04fca24d964","type":"text","text":"# Courtyard On-time\n\ntodo: The player arrives to the school's courtyard just in time to see Creeper addressing all of the students.\n\nnext:","x":-16815,"y":1197,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"ec6f1fe32d09fb93","type":"text","text":"# Courtyard Early\n\ntodo: The player arrives a little early and is approached by Magnet to talk.\n\nnext:","x":-16815,"y":1517,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"85f0b2c69d18fae6","type":"text","text":"# Friday Start\n\nPlayer wakes up and prepared for the prom.","x":1888,"y":1524,"width":337,"height":156,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"2c81a5c6ad338ba4","type":"text","text":"# Prom\n\nThe player attends prom. Either is approached or may approach others based on their reputation with them. Multiple endings based on reputations.","x":2302,"y":1448,"width":351,"height":309,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"c4e412cc87bcd244","type":"text","text":"# Ending Ideas\n","x":2813,"y":1448,"width":720,"height":618,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"6c2d1b95d00cb01e","type":"text","text":"# Courtyard\n\nAt the courtyard the player interacts with NOCs whose reactions are based on how and what they did at the competition.","x":720,"y":1267,"width":342,"height":220,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"70d0a913be621fca","type":"text","text":"# Day End\n\nThe day ends and the player goes to bed.","x":1190,"y":1296,"width":314,"height":162,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"7f36f2c802ee953c","type":"text","text":"# Start Wednesday\n\nThe player wakes up ready for the day ahead.","x":-2065,"y":1263,"width":371,"height":173,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"ed35a1836aea1cd2","type":"text","text":"# Courtyard\n\nIn the courtyard the player is jumpscared by the character they are closest to, letting them know about the datapacking competition being held today.","x":-1498,"y":1225,"width":347,"height":250,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"aa1ae14fc2cc2bf8","type":"text","text":"# The Competition \n\nDepending on the kind of datapacker caught and certain options made during the hunt the player is posed with different options during the competition. Its a kind of question mini game where the player decides on features and mechanics by plugging words into empty squares.","x":-338,"y":1197,"width":392,"height":359,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"426ee448a2096770","type":"text","text":"# Classroom\n\nIn the classroom creeper announces the competition and explains how it will work.","x":-950,"y":1263,"width":377,"height":200,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"045b1bda92436dc8","type":"text","text":"# The Judging\n\nCreeper judges the players datapack and the player gains or loses reputation with certain characters based on their options.","x":219,"y":1232,"width":329,"height":289,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"534d77dfc1cd3984","type":"text","text":"# The Park\n\nThe player takes the NPC out to the park. The NPC chooses what happens during this date.\n- Swan boat ride (Creeper,Femchro,Lead,Flux,Rag)\n- A Hike (Lead,Flux,Mystic,Primal,Creeper)\n- A picnic (Creeper,Femchro,Lead,Flux,Mystic,Rag)\n- Feed the ducks (Creeper,Lead,Flux,Rag,Primal)","x":-999,"y":2941,"width":502,"height":281,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"5e4185a5c0138e21","type":"text","text":"# Celebrity News\n\nDatapack celebrities jeeper and bedazzle supposedly dating???","x":-262,"y":3388,"width":360,"height":167,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"009070452feb3e2c","type":"text","text":"# News Broadcast (1)\n\nbackground: tvshow.celebrity.broadcaster\n\ntext: \"News Broadcaster: BREAKING NEWS!\"\n\ntext: \"News Broadcaster: Celebrities Jeeper and Bedazzle supposedly dating? Let's go to Samantha on the scene.\"\n\nbackground: tvshow.celebrity.samantha\n\ntext: \"Samantha: Yes Brad, this is just in now. We see here the two celebrities, Jeeper and Bedazzle, returning from a night on the town.\"\n\ntext: \"Samantha: The two were supposedly caught kissing in the back alley of a bread store, a member of the DPH tells us.\"\n\ntext: \"Samantha: Back to you, Brad.\"\n\nbackground: tvshow.celebrity.broadcaster\n\ntext: \"News Broadcaster: Wow. Truly astonishing what celebrities are allowed to get away with in the modern day.\"\n\ntext: \"News Broadcaster: Next up, 'Person Goes Missing on The Creeper's Campus', this and more at six.\"\n\nchoice:","x":175,"y":3402,"width":460,"height":760,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"2fdbc9a1607e14ef","type":"text","text":"# Date\n\nThe player goes out on a date with the character of their choice. Different characters may have different options.","x":-1473,"y":3149,"width":266,"height":263,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"cec510f513341189","type":"text","text":"# Let them decide\n\nThe player lets the NPC choose where they'll go for the date.\n- Primal: The gym.\n- Creeper: The library.\n- Flux: \n- Femchro: Beauty parlor.\n- Lead: The river (where they've been poisoning the water supply.)\n- Mystic: \n- Rag: ","x":-999,"y":3222,"width":502,"height":360,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"eaf7f9321c363dc9","type":"text","text":"# Galavant \n\nIt's galavant","x":-265,"y":3199,"width":265,"height":116,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"86f9d8270e730136","type":"text","text":"# Smithed Summit\n\nAd for the summit in town","x":319,"y":2512,"width":342,"height":153,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"8b2a68e0ae16f72e","type":"text","text":"# Datapack Hub\n\nAd with a bear roaring infront if a datapack hub sign.","x":319,"y":2699,"width":355,"height":152,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"074777ac124c0256","type":"text","text":"# Debate\n\nA political debate about datapack optimization.","x":-265,"y":2764,"width":338,"height":175,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"8c2f7c2040862752","type":"text","text":"# Loss\n\nTv show using the loss comic format.","x":-265,"y":2984,"width":306,"height":162,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"210dcdee8a431a03","type":"text","text":"# Idea\n\nPossible reference to Dave Hue alts during one of creeper's dates?","x":-1897,"y":3222,"width":250,"height":118,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"f93dac04f4b18ee0","type":"text","text":"# Hue & Hue Legal\n\nAd for hue & hue legal co.","x":330,"y":2147,"width":424,"height":166,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"8ca3bac6b25eda18","type":"text","text":"# Datapack Showcase\n\nYoutube style showcase that can showcase a random datapack","x":-265,"y":2540,"width":434,"height":196,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"03fa4d43b92b62cb","type":"text","text":"# Rad Cat\n\nidk something with rad","x":348,"y":3099,"width":250,"height":111,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"45b6247a7cd5098f","type":"text","text":"# Infomercial\n\nShow with dude marketing random datapack-related items.","x":-257,"y":2059,"width":355,"height":178,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"7e82a1500e8cfc7f","type":"text","text":"# Ad Break\n\nPicks a random ad to play, after ad has a 50% chance to end the tv watching period.","x":330,"y":1933,"width":347,"height":204,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"f2f6c728c3b6a8b5","type":"text","text":"# Talking Penguin\n\nad for a talking penguin doll","x":319,"y":2344,"width":342,"height":115,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"e6b72dd2f4e313a3","type":"text","text":"# TV Show\n\nPicks a show at random or based on criteria","x":-629,"y":2017,"width":320,"height":148,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"d989a260d94cfc24","type":"text","text":"# Alone Day\n\nIf the player does not get a phone call then they sit down to watch the television. A TV show is selected based on what character they have the highest reputation with.","x":-987,"y":1898,"width":266,"height":386,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"93eccb6192927e4f","type":"text","text":"# Day End\n\nThe day ends.","x":1175,"y":2667,"width":293,"height":139,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"6b478671d579cb1c","type":"text","text":"# Magnet Inc.\n\nAd about working for magnet inc.","x":341,"y":2886,"width":299,"height":161,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"8155a07ca90f0794","type":"text","text":"# Their Place\n\nThe player goes to the NPCs place.\n- Creepers: Tidy modern house\n- Lead: Takes you to the school storage closet.\n- Femchro: Barbie dream house mansion.\n- Flux: \n- Rag: \n- Primal: \n- Mystic: Egyptian pyramid crypt style house.","x":-999,"y":2589,"width":502,"height":350,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"b46d7d582546591a","type":"text","text":"# Ancient Aliens\n\nAncient aliens parody talking about the ancient technique of advancement packs","x":-257,"y":2284,"width":353,"height":192,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"234598c9efcc8964","type":"text","text":"# Creeper\n\nTv show based off that superhero dream i had ","x":-241,"y":1824,"width":286,"height":177,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"2ea8aa9d216fd703","type":"text","text":"# Restaurant\n\nThey go to a restaurant together. Each character can choose from their own shared pool of options.\n- Pizza joint (Creeper,Lead,Flux,Mystic,Primal,Rag)\n- Fancy restaurant (Creeper,Femchro,Lead,Rag)\n- Sushi bar (Creeper,Lead,Primal)\n- Picnic (Creeper,Femchro,Lead,Flux,Mystic,Rag)","x":-999,"y":2313,"width":502,"height":276,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"6c59dfcac296ce96","type":"text","text":"# Thursday Start\n\nPlayer wakes up and starts day.","x":-2117,"y":2019,"width":336,"height":226,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"1fe3deb9290d7217","type":"text","text":"# Phone Calls\n\nThe player receives phone calls from whichever characters they have achieved the proper reputation with. They may then choose which character to go out with.","x":-1509,"y":1980,"width":337,"height":304,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"79d484795d691c3c","type":"text","text":"# The Movies\n\nThe player takes them to the movies, and there are actual movies they watch together.\n- Attack of Frogzilla (Monkeyhue frogzilla monster feature)\n- John Smithed (John wick but with smithy)\n- Armor, stands (Doctor Who style weeping angle armorstands, reference to sethbling?)\n- Invasion of the Data Snatchers (Invasion of the Body Snatchers, but with \"Minecraft, But\" datapackers replacing good datapackers)","x":-999,"y":3582,"width":502,"height":368,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"2eaf284413475a03","type":"text","text":"# News Broadcast (1)\n\nbackground: tvshow.celebrity.broadcaster\n\ntext: \"News Broadcaster: BREAKING NEWS!\"\n\ntext: \"News Broadcaster: Celebrities Jeeper and Bedazzle supposedly dating? Let's go to Samantha on the scene.\"\n\nbackground: tvshow.celebrity.samantha\n\ntext: \"Samantha: Yes Brad, this is just in now. We see here the two celebrities, Jeeper and Bedazzle, returning from a night on the town.\"\n\ntext: \"Samantha: The two were supposedly caught kissing in the back alley of a bread store, a member of the DPH tells us.\"\n\ntext: \"Samantha: Back to you, Brad.\"\n\nbackground: tvshow.celebrity.broadcaster\n\ntext: \"News Broadcaster: Wow. Truly astonishing what celebrities are allowed to get away with in the modern day.\"\n\ntext: \"News Broadcaster: Next up, 'Person Goes Missing on The Creeper's Campus', this and more at six.\"\n\nchoice:","x":175,"y":4219,"width":460,"height":760,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"a459f8365baab792","type":"text","text":"# Wednesday\nWednesday is a data packing competition, where the players actions from the previous day regarding how they hunted the data packers impact their school work. \n\n---\n","x":-8023,"y":-8140,"width":346,"height":661,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"4af828c51f2031e1","type":"text","text":"# Tuesday\nTuesday is the player's first impressions with their new crush, as Creeper takes the class out on a fieldtrip to hunt a wild data packer. The players actions have big consequences on their crushes opinions on them during this day.\n\n---\n","x":-8400,"y":-8140,"width":346,"height":661,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"917b28ef5cf5c06d","type":"text","text":"# Monday\nMonday serves as the player's introduction to the game's cast of characters and the general setup for each day in the game. The allows the player to make a decision as to which character they most want to invest their time into.\n\n---\n","x":-8780,"y":-8140,"width":346,"height":661,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"78be5440e6fa5978","type":"text","text":"# Nexus\nMister Smithed himself, dean of The Creeper's College, is a renowned figure in the setting. Creator of Smithed Incorporated, a subsidiary of The Creeper Corporation.\n\nThey are a mysterious character, though their relation to Creeper seems ancient. They appear very formal.\n\nNexus Smithed does not appear often throughout the game, but their appearances drastically shift the narrative and raise tension.\n\n---","x":-8023,"y":-8840,"width":346,"height":661,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"125c4452dc4851c8","type":"text","text":"# Creeper\nProfessor Magnet is the players' and NPC's professor and owner of The Creeper's College, a barely disguised high school setting.\n\nMagnet is an amazing logical thinker, though suffers emotionally at times. He does not hold back when expressing disgust or hatred, though may seem reserved regarding other emotions.\n\nHe is a celebrity in the setting, known for his many past ventures. Creeper sees amazing opportunity in the player, having selected them for the school. As their professor he knows their love is wrong, but pursues it regardless.\n\n---\n","x":-8400,"y":-8840,"width":346,"height":661,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"8d66306db0aa3024","type":"text","text":"# Player\nThe player is a new student to TCCollege. The decisions they make with other characters determine their true personality and character history. Outside of this they are simply a studious person, or at least that's what Creeper thinks of them.\n\nThe decisions the player makes impact their reputation with the NPCs, impacting the way those NPCs interact with them and changing the end of the game.\n\n---\n","x":-8780,"y":-8840,"width":346,"height":661,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"3530b0ec0f196e4e","type":"text","text":"# Smithie\n\n\n---","x":-4240,"y":-8840,"width":346,"height":661,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"5aaa4e543d84aba5","type":"text","text":"# Scuttler\nThe Scuttler is the school pest, an invention by one of Creeper's previous, now-expelled, students. The Scuttler is encountered by the player in the school's courtyard as a feral pest, but a relationship may be pursued.\n\nTheir dating storyline parallels Lead's as a reversal of the trope. The Scuttler is sentient and possess language: though none of the NPCs believe the player. Players may translate the Scuttler's dialogue if they wish. NPCs believe the player's relationship to be abhorrent.\n\nThe Scuttler itself speaks in an animalistic broken form of English. It dubiously reciprocates the feelings of the player.\n\n---","x":-4620,"y":-8840,"width":346,"height":661,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"a73de73f9e075b5c","type":"text","text":"# Lead\nLead is a non-sentient ingot of pure lead. They do not possess any dialogue, expressing emotion only through their sprite. Despite this lack of dialogue the player may pursue romantic interest, which is not reciprocated by the ingot.\n\nLead's storylines revolve around the player not realizing that they are in fact not sentient and resulting in hijinks such as poisoning the towns water supply or giving innocent bystanders lead poisoning.\n\n---","x":-7260,"y":-8840,"width":346,"height":661,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"c43b6b16cc10706b","type":"text","text":"# Friday\nFriday is prom day, where the culmination of the player's actions result in different endings at the prom.\n\n---","x":-7260,"y":-8140,"width":346,"height":661,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"b6e8be797cfe0f94","type":"text","text":"# Thursday\nThursday the player takes their crush out on a date, though they may be turned down resulting in an alone-day. This day has a lot of different outcomes depending on who the player is interested in and their previous actions.\n\n---\n","x":-7642,"y":-8140,"width":346,"height":661,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"830c63f73fa2fe45","type":"text","text":"# Awesome\ntext: \"That's everything, I think!\"","x":-6497,"y":-9240,"width":346,"height":360,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"df130637a3873c48","type":"text","text":"# Text Examples\nbackground: player_bedroom(fade)\n\nsound: crash\n\nmusic: school_background\n\ntext: \"A generic text block is the narrator talking in-game!\"\n\nenter: creeper\n\ntext: creeper: \"This is how you make a character speak.\"\n\ntext: creeper(flustered): \"You can also change a characters emotion when they speak!\"\n\ncharacter: creeper(idle)\n\nexit: creeper\n\nreminder: You can add notes to the blocks which the converter will put into a txt file to tell you about later. You can also use 'note' instead of 'reminder'.\n\nnext:","x":-8780,"y":-9620,"width":346,"height":740,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"c4ecb130fbcbd371","type":"text","text":"# Player Choice\ntext: \"The \"next\" command moves to the next node. If there are multiple nodes following it it will choose a node randomly.\"\n\ntext: \"Next is the choice command.\"\n\nchoice: \"This is a choice.\": \\[\n\"That's cool\",\n\"That's not cool\"\n]","x":-8403,"y":-9620,"width":346,"height":740,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"8b9f0c99c7264a68","type":"text","text":"# Femchro\nFemchro is the typical high-energy quirky girl stereotype. Outwardly she appears to be what the player expects of this stereotype, but by pursuing her storyline the player may discover that despite her over-the-top aesthetic she is intelligent and capable—if a bit clumsy.\n\nShe has a naive and excited attitude generally, using a refined version of e-girl texting mannerisms. Despite this she is capable of having personal deep moments with the player.\n\nHer storylines may primarily revolve around mistakes she makes which the player must fix themselves. She has insecurities regarding the ways she's perceived by others and the way her own actions reinforce that perception.\n\nHer red flag is that she has a shrine of the player.\n\n---","x":-7642,"y":-8840,"width":346,"height":661,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"9807e9709b4dc19e","type":"text","text":"# Huh\ntext: \"Pretty cool, right? But what if we want to give the player a choice which changes based on a variable?\"\n\nnext:","x":-7260,"y":-9240,"width":346,"height":360,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"815dba1a8dc9e0be","type":"text","text":"# That's not cool\ntext: \"The title of the node are the text options presented to the player.\"\n\nnext:","x":-8022,"y":-9100,"width":346,"height":220,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"9ff401473317ae54","type":"text","text":"# What 'bout me?\ntext: \"Any text options not specified in the command are not shown. You can also leave the command as just one line to show all connected nodes.\"\n\nback:","x":-8022,"y":-9340,"width":346,"height":220,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"b8de1b7e7bbb1089","type":"text","text":"# That's cool\ntext: \"The choice command uses outcoming arrows from the parent node to determine what choices the player can make. The color of these arrows is meaningless.\"\n\nnext:","x":-8022,"y":-9620,"width":346,"height":260,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"2b516a883accde98","type":"text","text":"# Using Variables\ntext: \"Variables are a valuable tool for making branching paths and making characters feel real.\"\n\ntext: \"Here we go to the node titled \"Huh\" if the variable is greater than or equal to one, or \"Back?\" if it is less than one. If there are multiple arrows of the same color it chooses randomly.\"\n\nnext: \\[\n{if: read >= 1: \"Huh\"},\n{else: \"Back?\"}\n]\n\nnote: This is a conditional next command. It uses if statements and an else statement for if neither of the if statements return true. Else statements can be left blank, in which case they choose a random node which is not already mentioned in an if statement.\n","x":-7645,"y":-9620,"width":349,"height":740,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"11109463a9a6f784","type":"text","text":"# Back?\n\ntext: \"Back moves you back to the previous node. If there are multiple it chooses randomly.\"\n\nvar: read = 1\n\nback:","x":-7260,"y":-9620,"width":346,"height":360,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"e1a017749f30943f","type":"text","text":"# Variable Decision\ntext: \"This node will only display the choice of \"Awesome\" if you've already visited the node \"Let's go back\". True/False variables are quite simple to check for.\"\n\nchoice: \"Woah!\": \\[\n\"Let's go back\",\n{if: new.read = true: \"Awesome\"}\n]","x":-6880,"y":-9620,"width":346,"height":740,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"57e23269b5a14380","type":"text","text":"# Let's go back\ntext: \"Choices that arent specified in an if statement will appear regardless of any variables.\"\n\nflag: new.read = true\n\nback:","x":-6497,"y":-9620,"width":346,"height":360,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"b21183e6ca470125","type":"text","text":"# Femchro End Remarks\n\ntodo: Femchro reacts differently based on various factors.\n\nnext:","x":-7636,"y":578,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"f9fa8eaca80df48e","type":"text","text":"# Ragno End Remarks\n\ntodo: Ragno reacts differently based on various factors.\n\nnext:","x":-7636,"y":1178,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"08530124a54ea8d7","type":"text","text":"# Primal End Remarks\n\ntodo: Primal reacts differently based on various factors.\n\nnext:","x":-7636,"y":878,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"f0c291166955454b","type":"text","text":"# Creeper End Remarks\n\ntodo: Creeper reacts differently based on various factors.\n\nnext:","x":-7636,"y":1481,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"3158b5a3671e2578","type":"text","text":"# Closing Thoughts\n\ntodo: As the player walks home they think back on the day they just had. Before getting home and going to bed.\n\nnext:","x":-7086,"y":578,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"0c79157f7a3c05c2","type":"text","text":"# Smithed Interrupts Femchro\n\ntodo: Mr. Smithed greets Femchro and the player, commenting on their relationship.\n\nnext:","x":-8116,"y":578,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"100a1967f134550a","type":"text","text":"# Smithed Interrupts Primal\n\ntodo: Mr. Smithed greets Primal and the player, commenting on their relationship.\n\nnext:","x":-8116,"y":878,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"5f15658a70ad957d","type":"text","text":"# Lead End Remarks\n\ntodo: Lead remarks on absolute silence before leaving.\n\nnext:","x":-7636,"y":290,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"943f89768997239c","type":"text","text":"# Smithed Interrupts Ragno\n\ntodo: Mr. Smithed says that Ragno seems familiar, but can't quite place it. Comments on their relationship with the player.\n\nnext:","x":-8116,"y":1178,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"05c717806f355bcb","type":"text","text":"# Smithed Interrupts Creeper\n\ntodo: Mr. Smithed greets Magnet, questioning him on how the first day went for the new students. Questions player based on factors.\n\nnext:","x":-8116,"y":1481,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"f68772815c20af5e","type":"text","text":"# Lead Inquiry\n\ntodo: Player bumps into Lead in the courtyard and they greet each other. They are interrupted by Mister Smithed.\n\nnext:","x":-8576,"y":290,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"83b9210b14a91476","type":"text","text":"# Femchro Inquiry\n\ntodo: Femchro greets the player based on their previous interactions in the day, before being interrupted.\n\nnext:","x":-8576,"y":578,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"e0ed56256b3d3cae","type":"text","text":"# Smithed Interrupts Lead\n\ntodo: Mr. Smithed is dismissive of Lead's interactions. Focusing solely on the player.\n\nnext:","x":-8116,"y":290,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"15ad381085d10166","type":"text","text":"# Primal Inquiry\n\ntodo: Primal greets the player based on their previous interactions in the day, before being interrupted.\n\nnext:","x":-8576,"y":878,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"baf8ba25eb26c4d5","type":"text","text":"# Ragno Inquiry\n\ntodo: Ragno greets the player based on their previous interactions in the day, before being interrupted.\n\nnext:","x":-8576,"y":1178,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"6de0ca328d3c2fa5","type":"text","text":"# Sits With Ragno\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-9731,"y":1021,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"16b11a72652dbe4f","type":"text","text":"# Sits With Creeper\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-9731,"y":1324,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"03d0bcb6bd937985","type":"text","text":"# Enter Courtyard\n\ntodo: The player enters the courtyard of the school. Mister Smithed is giving a lecture. Afterwards the player is approached by whoever they sat next to during class.\n\nnext:","x":-9091,"y":721,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"ded2251b6ffa17f8","type":"text","text":"# Creeper Inquiry\n\ntodo: Creeper greets player based on their previous interactions in the day before being interrupted.\n\nnext:","x":-8576,"y":1481,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"d88f91bc29b5206c","type":"text","text":"# Sits Alone\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-9731,"y":1621,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"6ae34fc7d4326e30","type":"text","text":"# Sits With Femchro\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-9731,"y":421,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"071ad2cc857d7e13","type":"text","text":"# Sits With Primal\n\ntodo: \n\nnext:","x":-9731,"y":721,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"ad425b31e6a85ccc","type":"text","text":"# Ragno\nRagno, short for Ragnarokkr, is the harbinger of the apocalypse. Having snuck into the school their dating storyline revolves around their strange, sometimes overly sexual, tendencies.\n\nRagno attempts to appear as normal as possible, as a studious young woman looking to make their way in life. In actuality she is a hired assassin sent to destroy TCCollege and TCCorporation. Depending on the path the player takes dating her she attempts to destroy the school in various different ways.\n\nBy dating her the player can also manage to make her change her mind. Though this ending may be hard to achieve.\n\n---","x":-6877,"y":-8840,"width":346,"height":661,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"9f13dc64a6521274","type":"text","text":"# Mystic\nMystic is the school bully, though they do not attend the same class as the player—attending Modding Class instead of Data Packing Class. They are encountered outside of the main chunk of the player's day and are a dateable option. By dating Mystic the player encounters him more often.\n\nMystic is abrasive and a bit of a joker, misdirecting the player through pranks, jokes, and sarcasm. Though, when needed, they can easily adopt a serious attitude. The dating storyline for Mystic revolves around breaking down their emotional shield and revealing a more tender character.\n\n---","x":-6497,"y":-8840,"width":346,"height":661,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"1edccd2a7f9bcbb6","type":"text","text":"# Choose classmate\n\nchoice: \"With everyone's introductions out of the way and people beginning to pick their seats, who do you flock to?\"\n\nreminder: Recode this section to show all characters and allow the player to pick which character they want by clicking on said character.","x":-13860,"y":-5743,"width":420,"height":380,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"40ec6a2632cf79fc","type":"text","text":"# Sure.\n\ntext: creeper(idle): \"Is that sarcastic doubt I hear?\"\n\ntext: creeper(flustered): \"We'll see how far that gets you in this class.\"\n\ntext: \"Professor Magnet turns his attention to the room.\"\n\nnext:","x":-11730,"y":-2400,"width":459,"height":300,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"28f2f3118bcbe716","type":"text","text":"# Whatever.\n\ntext: creeper(disappointed): \"Yeah... Just let me know if you have any questions...\"\n\ntext: creeper(idle): \"You know, this class is quite difficult. Don't expect it to be easy.\"\n\nchoice:","x":-12269,"y":-2058,"width":460,"height":260,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"5c24751337795123","type":"text","text":"# Difficult? Nothing's hard for me.\n\ntext: creeper(flustered): \"Cocky today, are we?\"\n\ntext: creeper(idle): \"We'll see how you fare today.\"\n\ntext: \"Professor Magnet turns his head away from you and towards the whole class.\"\n\nnext:","x":-11730,"y":-2020,"width":459,"height":320,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"522b7a6e0cc645d8","type":"text","text":"# Alright.\n\ntext: creeper(idle): \"Yeah. Just let me know if you have any questions about the class.\"\n\ntext: creeper: \"You know, this class is quite difficult. Don't expect it to be easy.\"\n\nchoice:","x":-12269,"y":-2378,"width":460,"height":240,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"2e5d6d38bdc92f92","type":"text","text":"# Haha! Ok!\ntext: creeper(flustered): \"I like the enthusiasm!\"\n\ntext: creeper(idle): \"We'll have to find out how far it'll get you in this class.\"\n\ntext: \"Professor Magnet smirks at you as he turns his attention to the larger class behind you.\"\n\nnext:","x":-11730,"y":-2780,"width":459,"height":300,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"e0364fb241fb1cc6","type":"text","text":"# Oh, thanks!\n\ntext: creeper(idle): \"No problem! Just let me know if you have any questions about the class. It's a tough one, so don't expect me to go easy on you!\"\n\nchoice:","x":-12270,"y":-2678,"width":460,"height":220,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"ba7e7de8a33f79c7","type":"text","text":"# Chose Creeper\n\nenter: creeper\n\nvar: seat = 4\n\ntext: \"You take a seat next to the teacher's desk. Creeper is watching all the student chatter amongst themselves, and is pleasantly surprised when he looks over to see you sitting across from his desk!\"\n\ntext: creeper(flustered): \"Hey, [player_name]. Glad you sat here, it's the best seat to catch the presentations. If you miss anything don't forget that they're all uploaded onto the schools website too.\"\n\nchoice:","x":-12810,"y":-2478,"width":460,"height":440,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"17245f99a21307f9","type":"text","text":"# What's your name?\n\ntext: lead(flustered): \"...!!!\"\n\ntext: lead(shocked): \"...!\"\n\ntext: lead(idle): \"...\"\n\ntext: \"You're not entirely sure what they said, but you think they told you it's ok to just call them 'Lead'! That's an interesting name...\"\n\nnext:","x":-11180,"y":-5660,"width":460,"height":340,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"78c7cb08256ede92","type":"text","text":"# Do you talk?\n\ntext: lead(disappointed): \".....\"\n\ntext: lead(idle): \"...\"\n\ntext: \"You don't know exactly what they're telling you, but you think they're saying they can't talk.\"\n\nnext:","x":-11180,"y":-5240,"width":460,"height":280,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"bd5cf9feff4000aa","type":"text","text":"# Are you new here?\n\ntext: lead(flustered): \"...!\"\n\ntext: lead(idle): \"...\"\n\ntext: lead(disappointed): \"......\"\n\ncharacter: lead(idle)\n\ntext: \"You can't tell what they're saying, but you think they said that this is their first semester! The two of you share so much in common!\"\n\nnext:","x":-11180,"y":-4880,"width":460,"height":380,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"cdb7d6f90c4f65a0","type":"text","text":"# Hi!\n\ntext: \"Your remark falls on deaf ears, the ingot makes no attempt to react; it remains lifelessly still atop the table. Now that you're closer though you take the opportunity to examine the ingot's make!\"\n\ntext: \"It appears to be made from Lead. As you go to touch it it finally notices you.\"\n\ntext: lead(flustered): \"...!\"\n\nchoice:","x":-12260,"y":-5730,"width":460,"height":360,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"5f14f4f55e497fb8","type":"text","text":"# Why are you seated so far from the front?\n\ntext: \"Your question falls on deaf ears, the ingot makes no attempt to react; it remains lifelessly still atop the table. Now that you're closer though you take the opportunity to examine the ingot's make!\"\n\ntext: \"It appears to be made from Lead. As you go to touch it it finally notices you.\"\n\ntext: lead(flustered): \"...!\"\n\nchoice:","x":-12260,"y":-5290,"width":460,"height":380,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"5de4867d2e827966","type":"text","text":"# How's that weather?\n\ntext: \"Your question falls on deaf ears, the ingot makes no attempt to react; it remains lifelessly still atop the table. Now that you're closer though you take the opportunity to examine the ingot's make!\"\n\ntext: \"It appears to be made from Lead. As you go to touch it it finally notices you.\"\n\ntext: lead(flustered): \"...!\"\n\nchoice:","x":-12260,"y":-4830,"width":460,"height":360,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"063e8fa8308d3b91","type":"text","text":"# Oh! Hello!\n\ntext: lead: \"...\"\n\ntext: lead(idle): \"...\"\n\ntext: \"Despite their mute nature they appear to be communicating through visual cues. The exact mechanics by how this works are not entirely obvious to you, but it is successful.\"\n\nchoice:","x":-11720,"y":-5490,"width":460,"height":320,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"0ae8d91ee3d72c30","type":"text","text":"# ... Hi?\n\ntext: lead(disappointed): \"...\"\n\ntext: lead(idle): \"...\"\n\ntext: lead(flustered): \"...\"\n\ncharacter: lead(idle)\n\ntext: \"Despite their mute nature they appear to be communicating through visual cues. The exact mechanics by how this works are not entirely obvious to you, but it is successful.\"\n\nchoice:","x":-11720,"y":-5010,"width":460,"height":400,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"12034844b24c059c","type":"text","text":"# Chose Lead\n\nenter: lead\n\nvar: seat = 2\n\ntext: \"You take a seat next to the Ingot. Strangely they're positioned at the back of the classroom, sitting on top of a foldup table next to the utility closet. The room is full of noise as students chatter amongst each other.\"\n\ntext: lead(idle): \"...\"\n\nchoice:","x":-12800,"y":-5280,"width":460,"height":360,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"0fd8940152f0bbad","type":"text","text":"# Recursion\n\nchoice: \"What is recursion?\":","x":-8876,"y":-4126,"width":380,"height":110,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"59208b9b23364b3d","type":"text","text":"# Recursion End\n\ntext: \"You're a little familiar with the basics of data packing.\"\n\nnext:","x":-7957,"y":-4161,"width":380,"height":180,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"c587d698049fc4ff","type":"text","text":"# The process of a function calling itself.\n\nvar: test_score + 1\n\nnext:","x":-8416,"y":-3901,"width":380,"height":200,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"d217f9e84221b53a","type":"text","text":"# A function that loops through data until a condition is met.\n\nnext:","x":-8416,"y":-4161,"width":380,"height":180,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"5ae086cf76e33c43","type":"text","text":"# This\n\nvar: test_score + 1\n\nback:","x":-8416,"y":-4381,"width":380,"height":140,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"b99b0f4dd5708efc","type":"text","text":"# Organ Transportation\n\nchoice: \"What is the proper way to store an organ for transportation?\":","x":-8876,"y":-5061,"width":380,"height":131,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"1883b4becbbab934","type":"text","text":"# Submerging it in a saline solution and placing it in a sealed cool container.\n\nvar: test_score + 1\n\nnext:","x":-8416,"y":-5321,"width":380,"height":280,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"09a7470e1a2d43c3","type":"text","text":"# Organ Transportation End\n\ntext: \"You're a little unsure as to why this question is on the test at all. What does transporting organs have to do with packing data?\"\n\nnext:","x":-7957,"y":-5135,"width":380,"height":280,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"a0fc3e99242b1a4c","type":"text","text":"# @a\n\nnext:","x":-8416,"y":-2396,"width":380,"height":100,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"9ac4745b621adb9e","type":"text","text":"# Selector end - close\n\ntext: \"That question was tough, but you think you nailed it!\"\n\nnext:","x":-7957,"y":-2231,"width":380,"height":170,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"7f80ad2392dc02ba","type":"text","text":"# @s\n\nvar: test_score + 1\n\nnext:","x":-8416,"y":-2216,"width":380,"height":140,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"c9df28fb5b1be653","type":"text","text":"# @n\n\nnext:","x":-8416,"y":-2001,"width":380,"height":100,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"c40111bb0974e6f4","type":"text","text":"# @e\n\nnext:","x":-8416,"y":-2936,"width":380,"height":100,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"975c77e8827be46e","type":"text","text":"# Selector end - wrong\n\ntext: \"That question was tough! You're not quite sure if you got it right, but you hope so!\"\n\nnext:","x":-7957,"y":-2807,"width":380,"height":207,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"fe25b9e68b8e8599","type":"text","text":"# @r\n\nnext:","x":-8416,"y":-2756,"width":380,"height":105,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"f19cdcbd07039dd4","type":"text","text":"# Selector\n\nchoice: \"You've previously used the target selector @e to arbitrarily select all entities that match the criteria of an unspecified target selector argument. What selector should be used in subsequent functions for optimal performance when the intention is to execute the command(s) as each selected entity?\":","x":-8876,"y":-2673,"width":380,"height":295,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"51c0e0705030e78d","type":"text","text":"# @p\n\nnext:","x":-8416,"y":-2576,"width":380,"height":100,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"42a992235f96d0d5","type":"text","text":"# Meaning of life\n\nchoice: \"What is the meaning of life?\":","x":-8876,"y":-3321,"width":380,"height":100,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"714132d4384f1f91","type":"text","text":"# Life's meaning is subjective.\n\nnext:","x":-8416,"y":-3541,"width":380,"height":140,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"63091bf0f75d7123","type":"text","text":"# 42.\n\nnext:","x":-8416,"y":-3321,"width":380,"height":105,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"3cc9c0df936f9fc8","type":"text","text":"# To pass this test.\n\nnext:","x":-8416,"y":-3141,"width":380,"height":100,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"21b1d74525989733","type":"text","text":"# Bad rep\n\ntext: \"Professor Magnet slams a large stack of the tests onto the desk in front of you. You're unsure why its so large since there aren't that many students behind you. You struggle to lift the stack as you pass it to the next student.\"\n\nnext:","x":-9936,"y":-3807,"width":420,"height":260,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"a6e118ec92068bba","type":"text","text":"# Meaning of life end\n\ntext: \"You're completely stumped as to why Professor Magnet would include a question like that on the quiz? Is that question even on the other's tests?\"\n\nnext:","x":-7957,"y":-3391,"width":380,"height":240,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"62179122ca8b1a06","type":"text","text":"# Isn't in front\n\ntext: \"You watch as Professor Magnet hands the tests to the students at the front and they pass them backwards. You're a little nervous, but you're sure you'll be fine.\"\n\nnext: \\[\n{if: seat = 1: \"Femchro affirmation\"},\n{if: seat = 2: \"Lead affirmation\"},\n{if: seat = 3: \"Ragno affirmation\"},\n{else: \"How?\"}\n]","x":-9936,"y":-3487,"width":420,"height":410,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"cb8757aa87a55203","type":"text","text":"# Good rep\n\ntext: \"Professor Magnet gently hands you a stack of the tests, which are surprisingly heavy for some paper. Despite having no face you can tell he's giving you a gentle smile.\"\n\ntext: creeper(flustered): \"Good luck with the test!\"\n\nnext:","x":-9936,"y":-4167,"width":420,"height":280,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"f4fc553d631e4665","type":"text","text":"# The 'Triple-Bagging' method.\n\nnext:","x":-8416,"y":-4961,"width":380,"height":140,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"f3c1a4163be3c7da","type":"text","text":"# Rinse in warm sterile water before packing into a cool sealed container.\n\nnext:","x":-8416,"y":-4741,"width":380,"height":220,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"5d974f0fba888303","type":"text","text":"# Is in front\n\nnext: \\[\n{if: creeper_upset = false: \"Good rep\"},\n{else: \"Bad rep\"}\n]","x":-9936,"y":-4427,"width":420,"height":180,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"da1bedbec42081d4","type":"text","text":"# Femchro affirmation\n\ntext: femchro(flustered): \"You look a little nervous! But I'm sure you've got this!\"\n\nexit: femchro\n\nnext:","x":-9436,"y":-4600,"width":420,"height":224,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"61a17a941338d3b3","type":"text","text":"# Lead affirmation\n\ntext: lead: \"!!!\"\n\ntext: lead(idle): \"...\"\n\nexit: lead\n\nnext:","x":-9436,"y":-4296,"width":420,"height":244,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"0d97fabfb9b23599","type":"text","text":"# Freeze the organ in a block of dry ice.\n\nnext:","x":-8416,"y":-5541,"width":380,"height":140,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"e61762e3b639a2f7","type":"text","text":"# Creeper announces test\n\nenter: creeper\n\ntext: creeper(idle): \"Alright, now that everyone has had the opportunity to introduce themselves and take a seat we'll start the year off right; with a placement test.\"\n\ntext: creeper(flustered): \"The purpose of this test is for me to gauge each of your overall levels of knowledge regarding data packing...\"\n\ntext: creeper(idle): \"...\"\n\ntext: creeper: \"... With that said, you should *absolutely* be afraid of failure. Failure is not tolerated in this class. Anyone who scores below a passing grade will be verbally ridiculed Infront of the entire auditorium.\"\n\ntext: creeper(flustered): \"Now, I will hand the papers off to the students in the front of each row. Please keep one test and pass the rest back to the students behind yourselves.\"\n\ntext: creeper(idle): \"Please do not begin the tests until instructed to do so.\"\n\nnext: \\[\n{if: seat = 6: \"Is in front\"},\n{else: \"Isn't in front\"}\n]","x":-10496,"y":-4174,"width":479,"height":735,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"0939595311f662c3","type":"text","text":"# To end all currently running scripts and return the result of the last command.\n\nnext:","x":-6777,"y":-3121,"width":380,"height":220,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"277b09fab0f6dade","type":"text","text":"# To execute a command across all applicable targets.\n\nnext:","x":-6777,"y":-2821,"width":380,"height":180,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"420c23b416bdc905","type":"text","text":"# Tags end\n\ntext: \"Tags are a really useful tool when data packing, you just hope you remembered how to use them!\"\n\nnext:","x":-6317,"y":-2204,"width":380,"height":204,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"f5c374a6ff52c5fe","type":"text","text":"# To classify entities for easier targeting.\n\nvar: test_score + 1\n\nnext:","x":-6777,"y":-2061,"width":380,"height":200,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"5d6b1e55adff57c2","type":"text","text":"# To render an entity immune to events.\n\nnext:","x":-6777,"y":-1781,"width":380,"height":140,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"723e8ac88d5466a2","type":"text","text":"# To bind an entity to a function.\n\nnext:","x":-6777,"y":-2501,"width":380,"height":140,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"96918c9867914b18","type":"text","text":"# To apply textures to entities dynamically.\n\nnext:","x":-6777,"y":-2281,"width":380,"height":140,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"2f70b3865bced78d","type":"text","text":"# Tags\n\nchoice: \"What is the purpose of entity tags?\":","x":-7237,"y":-2167,"width":380,"height":129,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"256322f043916bec","type":"text","text":"# To run commands under or during specific conditions.\nvar: test_score + 1\n\nnext:","x":-6777,"y":-3661,"width":380,"height":240,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"00a4f2d406b9a578","type":"text","text":"# To go before commands.\n\nnext:","x":-6777,"y":-3335,"width":380,"height":134,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"db14c5b140c41c85","type":"text","text":"# Execute end\n\ntext: \"Execute is a very complex command, so you're glad they're not asking about syntax! You hope you got that question right!\"\n\nnext:","x":-6317,"y":-3279,"width":380,"height":245,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"6a09f81ee3613ca2","type":"text","text":"# Execute\n\nchoice: \"What is the purpose of the execute command?\":","x":-7237,"y":-3221,"width":380,"height":129,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"9e38eeaed7767247","type":"text","text":"# To get, merge, modify, or remove NBT from an entity or storage.\n\nvar: test_score + 1\n\nnext:","x":-6777,"y":-4541,"width":380,"height":240,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"b7099c05f72268b9","type":"text","text":"# Data end\n\ntext: \"That one was easy, you think you nailed it!\"\n\nnext:","x":-6317,"y":-4225,"width":380,"height":189,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"e86aef2fdbd9e7a2","type":"text","text":"# To execute commands stored in other data files.\n\nnext:","x":-6777,"y":-4220,"width":380,"height":179,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"75094c3a708c194e","type":"text","text":"# Data\n\nchoice: \"What is the purpose of the data command?\":","x":-7237,"y":-4195,"width":380,"height":129,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"a36c0fc331fee749","type":"text","text":"# To take up too much of the servers tick.\n\nnext:","x":-6777,"y":-3961,"width":380,"height":140,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"260c16d60907aaa4","type":"text","text":"# Scoreboard end\n\ntext: \"It's been a while since you've used scoreboards, but that question was too tough!\"\n\nnext:","x":-6317,"y":-5181,"width":380,"height":200,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"d078f3f5adb3f016","type":"text","text":"# Scoreboard\n\nchoice: \"Which of the following uses the proper syntax for the 'scoreboard' command?\":","x":-7237,"y":-5161,"width":380,"height":160,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"28ffbc15cfc35f42","type":"text","text":"# /scoreboard players set temp @s 1\n\nnext:","x":-6777,"y":-5041,"width":380,"height":140,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"26920b3463aa024c","type":"text","text":"# /scoreboard set players temp @s 1\n\nnext:","x":-6777,"y":-4821,"width":380,"height":140,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"e139812d3d312eb8","type":"text","text":"# /scoreboard set players temp 1\n\nnext:","x":-6777,"y":-5260,"width":380,"height":139,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"7ca342bd6f1e3ed6","type":"text","text":"# /scoreboard players set @s temp 1\n\nvar: test_score + 1\n\nnext:","x":-6777,"y":-5541,"width":380,"height":200,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"dc769140947dc78a","type":"text","text":"# Ragno affirmation\n\ntext: ragno(flustered): \"Looking a little nervous? You've probably got this.\"\n\nexit: ragno\n\nnext:","x":-9436,"y":-3980,"width":420,"height":219,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"7855edee62e1e9e6","type":"text","text":"# How?\n\ntext: \"IDK how you got here, but congrats, you broke the game!\"\n\nnext:","x":-9436,"y":-3677,"width":420,"height":219,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"3379b55119ec0667","type":"text","text":"# Start Test\n\ntext: creeper(flustered): \"Alright, everyone. I expect complete silence in the classroom once the test begins—which will be right now.\"\n\ntext: \"The classroom goes silent as everyone looks down to their tests. The only thing you hear is the scratching of pen on paper in-between the slightly elevated beating of your own heart.\"\n\nvar: test_score = 0\n\nnext:","x":-9436,"y":-3399,"width":420,"height":366,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"35f81c99872a7093","type":"text","text":"# Selector node\n\nreminder: Remember to make this node randomly select a question but not let the same question be asked twice. Also, if possible, change the test to appear as an actual paper test in the game.","x":-9400,"y":-2961,"width":349,"height":251,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"2abf0019fe632657","type":"text","text":"# Mystic Interrupts Lead\n\ntodo: Mystic interrupts the player's interaction with Lead. The player can choose to either stand up and fight back or forfeit their money to Mystic. Lead judges the player accordingly.\n\nnext:","x":850,"y":-4703,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"3c8241e789bf12a8","type":"text","text":"# Lead End Interaction\n\ntodo: Closing remarks from Lead as they leave the cafeteria. The player follows out to the courtyard of the school.\n\nnext:","x":1270,"y":-4703,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"f60e3b915d491999","type":"text","text":"# Forgot Lunchbox\n\ntodo: Player enters cafeteria and remembers they forgot their lunchbox. They're given the choice to either not eat or purchase food.\n\nnext:","x":-1010,"y":-4791,"width":380,"height":1098,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"203e8b3f475e19e9","type":"text","text":"# Get Food\n\ntodo: The player decides to get food. They choose which kind.\n\nnext:","x":-550,"y":-4791,"width":380,"height":220,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"33b7d91c30391dd2","type":"text","text":"# Don't Get Food\n\ntodo: The player is hungry. But they sit it out.\n\nnext:","x":-550,"y":-4491,"width":380,"height":200,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"d24c9214e7c38430","type":"text","text":"# Chose Food\n\ntodo: This would be multiple blocks depending on the food the player selects. \n\nnext:","x":-550,"y":-4211,"width":380,"height":219,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"b06e2d59b192d916","type":"text","text":"# NPC Joins Table\n\ntodo: A random student NPC who is NOT the one the player sat next to in class joins the player at their lunch table.\n\nnext:","x":-531,"y":-3911,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"749455a871e1d536","type":"text","text":"# Brought Lunchbox\n\ntodo: Player enters the cafeteria. They have their lunchbox\n\nnext:","x":-1010,"y":-3574,"width":380,"height":906,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"f5d293e1d0351a7a","type":"text","text":"# Lead Start Interaction\n\ntodo: Lead joins the player at the table. They speak in a typical lead way.\n\nnext:","x":-8,"y":-4703,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"cfa84bb37f35a3ae","type":"text","text":"# Lead Judges Food\n\ntodo: Lead reacts to the player based on their choice of food.\n\nnext:","x":430,"y":-4703,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"b054815e582ea2ef","type":"text","text":"# Smithed Interrupts Lead\n\ntodo: Mr. Smithed is dismissive of Lead's interactions. Focusing solely on the player.\n\nnext:","x":-45,"y":-2051,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"3c06e53a6702f828","type":"text","text":"# Lead End Remarks\n\ntodo: Lead remarks on absolute silence before leaving.\n\nnext:","x":435,"y":-2051,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"7c5b85cceeb45ae5","type":"text","text":"# Lead Inquiry\n\ntodo: Player bumps into Lead in the courtyard and they greet each other. They are interrupted by Mister Smithed.\n\nnext:","x":-505,"y":-2051,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"fd80021c62530107","type":"text","text":"# Enter Courtyard\n\ntodo: The player enters the courtyard of the school. Mister Smithed is giving a lecture. Afterwards the player is approached by whoever they sat next to during class.\n\nnext:","x":-1020,"y":-1320,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"4990fb9aa665a64b","type":"text","text":"# Closing Thoughts\n\ntodo: As the player walks home they think back on the day they just had. Before getting home and going to bed.\n\nnext:","x":985,"y":-1463,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"9d8dcf1bb6cfe8c2","type":"text","text":"# Creeper Dumbfounded\n\ntext: \"Professor Magnet finishes giving his closing statements regarding the test and future expectations before approaching you.\"\n\ntext: creeper(flustered): \"Congratulations! That was amazing! I have no idea how you managed to score that high? You'll definitely have to clue me in later.\"\n\nsound: class_bell\n\ntext: \"The bell rings, dismissing the class. You find it strange that this college has such a strange high-school-like practice...\"\n\ntext: creeper(idle): \"You should go get to the cafeteria! I can't imagine the calories you need to consume to power a brain like yours!\"\n\nexit: creeper\n\ntext: \"You leave Professor Magnet behind, exiting the classroom and entering the crowded school hallways.\"\n\nnext:","x":-3730,"y":-2858,"width":380,"height":720,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"0a0b32de8676f9d9","type":"text","text":"# Creeper Congratulates\n\ntext: \"Professor Magnet finishes giving his closing statements regarding the test and future expectations before approaching you.\"\n\ntext: creeper(flustered): \"Great work! You scored pretty well amongst all the other students. I was right to think you would be a good fit in this class.\"\n\nsound: class_bell\n\ntext: \"The bell rings, dismissing the class. You find it strange that this college has such a strange high-school-like practice...\"\n\ntext: creeper: \"You should probably start headed to the cafeteria now, the halls are going to be monstrous if you wait too long!\"\n\nexit: creeper\n\ntext: \"You leave Professor Magnet behind, exiting the classroom and entering the crowded school hallways.\"\n\nnext:","x":-3270,"y":-2858,"width":380,"height":720,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"1665c9ce57ae9d01","type":"text","text":"# Creeper Consoles\n\ntext: \"Professor Magnet finishes giving his closing statements regarding the test and future expectations before approaching you.\"\n\ntext: creeper(disappointed): \"I was expecting better from you, but at least you passed. You're going to need to work on this in the future.\"\n\nsound: class_bell\n\ntext: \"The bell rings, dismissing the class. You find it strange that this college has such a strange high-school-like practice...\"\n\ntext: creeper(idle): \"You should get moving, the halls are going to be monstrous.\"\n\nexit: creeper\n\ntext: \"You leave Professor Magnet behind, exiting the classroom and entering the crowded school hallways.\"\n\nnext:","x":-2810,"y":-2858,"width":380,"height":720,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"fb05ae392f7cb97f","type":"text","text":"# Creeper Disgusted\n\ntext: \"Professor Magnet finishes giving his closing statements regarding the test and future expectations before approaching you.\"\n\ntext: creeper(surprised): \"Wow... I don't even know what to say?\"\n\nsound: class_bell\n\ntext: \"The bell rings, dismissing the class. You find it strange that this college has such a strange high-school-like practice...\"\n\ntext: creeper(disappointed): \"I was really expecting so much more from you... You should go...\"\n\nexit: creeper\n\ntext: \"You begrudgingly leave Professor Magnet behind, exiting the classroom and entering the crowded school hallways.\"\n\nnext:","x":-2350,"y":-2858,"width":385,"height":720,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"db5de3c6e96ce884","type":"text","text":"# Lead Dumbfounded\n\nenter: lead\n\ntext: \"As Professor Magnet finishes and gives his closing statements and expectations moving forward Lead reaches out to you.\"\n\nexit: creeper\n\ntext: lead(surprised): \"!!!\"\n\ntext: lead(idle): \"...!\"\n\nsound: class_bell\n\ntext: \"The bell rings, dismissing the class. You find it strange that this college has such a strange high-school-like practice...\"\n\ntext: lead: \"...!\"\n\nexit: lead\n\ntext: \"Lead stops talking and sinks back into the table which they sit atop.\"\n\ntext: \"You figure they must be resting, and so gather your belongings from your desk and exit the classroom to meet everyone in the school's corridors.\"\n\nnext:","x":-3730,"y":-3718,"width":380,"height":760,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"6e49fd030930f492","type":"text","text":"# Lead Congratulates\n\nenter: lead\n\ntext: \"As Professor Magnet finishes and gives his closing statements and expectations moving forward Lead reaches out to you.\"\n\nexit: creeper\n\ntext: lead(surprised): \"!!!\"\n\ntext: lead(idle): \"......!\"\n\nsound: class_bell\n\ntext: \"The bell rings, dismissing the class. You find it strange that this college has such a strange high-school-like practice...\"\n\ntext: lead: \"...!\"\n\nexit: lead\n\ntext: \"Lead stops talking and sinks back into the table which they sit atop.\"\n\ntext: \"You figure they must be resting, and so gather your belongings from your desk and exit the classroom to meet everyone in the school's corridors.\"\n\nnext:","x":-3270,"y":-3718,"width":380,"height":760,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"b29ce0e09c561d1e","type":"text","text":"# Lead Consoles\n\nenter: lead\n\ntext: \"As Professor Magnet finishes and gives his closing statements and expectations moving forward Lead reaches out to you.\"\n\nexit: creeper\n\ntext: lead(shocked): \"!!!?\"\n\ntext: lead(idle): \"...!\"\n\nsound: class_bell\n\ntext: \"The bell rings, dismissing the class. You find it strange that this college has such a strange high-school-like practice...\"\n\ntext: lead: \"...!\"\n\nexit: lead\n\ntext: \"Lead stops talking and sinks back into the table which they sit atop.\"\n\ntext: \"You figure they must be resting, and so gather your belongings from your desk and exit the classroom to meet everyone in the school's corridors.\"\n\nnext:","x":-2810,"y":-3718,"width":380,"height":760,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"101bc3178cc5e17f","type":"text","text":"# Lead Disgusted\n\nenter: lead\n\ntext: \"As Professor Magnet finishes and gives his closing statements and expectations moving forward Lead reaches out to you.\"\n\nexit: creeper\n\ntext: lead(disappointed): \"???\"\n\ntext: lead(surprised): \"...?\"\n\nsound: class_bell\n\ntext: \"The bell rings, dismissing the class. You find it strange that this college has such a strange high-school-like practice...\"\n\ntext: lead: \"...!?\"\n\nexit: lead\n\ntext: \"Lead stops talking and sinks back into the table which they sit atop.\"\n\ntext: \"You figure they must be resting, and so gather your belongings from your desk and exit the classroom to meet everyone in the school's corridors.\"\n\nnext:","x":-2350,"y":-3718,"width":380,"height":760,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"4c10781fa0830a00","type":"text","text":"# Femchro Disgusted\n\nenter: femchro\n\ntext: \"As Professor Magnet finishes and gives his closing statements and expectations moving forward Femchro reaches out to you.\"\n\nexit: creeper\n\ntext: femchro(disappointed): \"Youch! That's got to sting... You seemed promising, but alas, I suppose it was not meant to be...\"\n\nexit: femchro\n\nsound: class_bell\n\ntext: \"The bell rings, dismissing the class. You watch as Femchro scurries out the door of the class into the hallway. You're a little confused as to why this college has a bell to dismiss classes, but it's hard to think about that between the absolute terror you are currently feeling.\"\n\ntext: \"As you exit the classroom and enter the college's corridors you cant help but be almost entirely consumed by the thought of your complete and utter failure as a student.\"\n\nnext:","x":-2350,"y":-4658,"width":380,"height":820,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"ecfc527ebec6621c","type":"text","text":"# Femchro Dumbfounded\n\nenter: femchro\n\ntext: \"As Professor Magnet finishes and gives his closing statements and expectations moving forward Femchro reaches out to you.\"\n\nexit: creeper\n\ntext: femchro(flustered): \"Wow! How'd you manage that!? You must be, like, amazing!\"\n\nsound: class_bell\n\ntext: \"The bell rings, dismissing the class. You find it strange that this college has such strange high-school-like practice...\"\n\ntext: femchro(entrance): \"Oh~! I've got to go! I'll see you later! Toodaloo!\"\n\nexit: femchro\n\ntext: \"Without further notice Femchro dashes out the classroom door, disappearing into the halls.\"\n\ntext: \"You follow behind her, gathering your belongings from your desk and meeting everyone in the school's corridors.\"\n\nnext:","x":-3730,"y":-4658,"width":380,"height":820,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"25ed9b89328a0034","type":"text","text":"# Femchro Congratulates\n\nenter: femchro\n\ntext: \"As Professor Magnet finishes and gives his closing statements and expectations moving forward Femchro reaches out to you.\"\n\nexit: creeper\n\ntext: femchro(idle): \"Dang! You did pretty good! Way better than me!\"\n\nsound: class_bell\n\ntext: \"The bell rings, dismissing the class. You find it strange that this college has such a strange high-school-like practice...\"\n\ntext: femchro(entrance): \"Oh~! Got to go! I'll see you later! Toodaloo!\"\n\nexit: femchro\n\ntext: \"Without further notice Femchro dashes out the classroom door, disappearing into the halls.\"\n\ntext: \"You follow behind her, gathering your belongings from your desk and meeting everyone in the school's corridors.\"\n\nnext:","x":-3270,"y":-4658,"width":380,"height":820,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"9093078180e4c644","type":"text","text":"# Femchro Consoles\n\nenter: femchro\n\ntext: \"As Professor Magnet finishes and gives his closing statements and expectations moving forward Femchro reaches out to you.\"\n\nexit: creeper\n\ntext: femchro(surprised): \"Yikes! Well, at least it wasn't the worst score in the class! I'm sure you'll nail the future assignments!\"\n\nsound: class_bell\n\ntext: \"The school bell rings, dismissing the class. You find it strange that this college has such a strange high-school-esque practice...\"\n\ntext: femchro(entrance): \"Oh! I've got to go! See ya' on the flip side!\"\n\nexit: femchro\n\ntext: \"Femchro runs out the classroom door disappearing into the halls into the crowd of students.\"\n\ntext: \"You follow in her tracks, gathering your belongings and meeting the crowd of students gathered in the corridor.\"\n\nnext:","x":-2810,"y":-4658,"width":380,"height":820,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"5bbc448d0db37335","type":"text","text":"# Ragno Dumbfounded\n\nenter: ragno\n\ntext: \"As Professor Magnet finishes and gives his closing statements and expectations moving forward Primal reaches out to you.\"\n\nexit: creeper\n\ntext: ragno(surprised): \"Wow. You really are one of the best, aren't you?\"\n\nsound: class_bell\n\ntext: \"The bell rings, dismissing the class. You find it strange that this college has such a strange high-school-like practice...\"\n\ntext: ragno(idle): \"I'll be seeing you later, [player_name].\"\n\nexit: ragno\n\ntext: \"Ragno rushes out the classroom door, disappearing into the crowded halls of students.\"\n\ntext: \"You follow in his tracks, gathering your belongings and meeting the crowd of students gathered in the corridor.\"\n\nnext:","x":-3730,"y":-5558,"width":380,"height":780,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"b71d15030fec1eba","type":"text","text":"# Ragno Congratulates\n\nenter: ragno\n\ntext: \"As Professor Magnet finishes and gives his closing statements and expectations moving forward Primal reaches out to you.\"\n\nexit: creeper\n\ntext: ragno(surprised): \"Good job. You're pretty good for what you do.\"\n\nsound: class_bell\n\ntext: \"The bell rings, dismissing the class. You find it strange that this college has such a strange high-school-like practice...\"\n\ntext: ragno(idle): \"I'll be seeing you, [player_name].\"\n\nexit: ragno\n\ntext: \"Ragno rushes out the classroom door, disappearing into the crowded halls of students.\"\n\ntext: \"You follow in his tracks, gathering your belongings and meeting the crowd of students gathered in the corridor.\"\n\nnext:","x":-3270,"y":-5545,"width":380,"height":767,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"142d9bd01311f7c1","type":"text","text":"# Ragno Consoles\n\nenter: ragno\n\ntext: \"As Professor Magnet finishes and gives his closing statements and expectations moving forward Primal reaches out to you.\"\n\nexit: creeper\n\ntext: ragno(idle): \"Well, it's not the worst score in the class, is it? I'm sure you were just nervous.\"\n\nsound: class_bell\n\ntext: \"The bell rings, dismissing the class. You find it strange that this college has such a strange high-school-like practice...\"\n\ntext: ragno(idle): \"See you around.\"\n\nexit: ragno\n\ntext: \"Ragno rushes out the classroom door, disappearing into the crowded halls of students.\"\n\ntext: \"You follow in his tracks, gathering your belongings and meeting the crowd of students gathered in the corridor.\"\n\nnext:","x":-2810,"y":-5545,"width":380,"height":767,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"1d6d919870119fc8","type":"text","text":"# Ragno Disgusted\n\nenter: ragno\n\ntext: \"As Professor Magnet finishes and gives his closing statements and expectations moving forward Primal reaches out to you.\"\n\nexit: creeper\n\ntext: ragno(disappointed): \"Holy—you really are stupid, aren't you? I overestimated your ability...\"\n\nsound: class_bell\n\ntext: \"The bell rings, dismissing the class. You find it strange that this college has such a strange high-school-like practice...\"\n\ntext: ragno: \"I'll be seeing you later.\"\n\nexit: ragno\n\ntext: \"Ragno rushes out the classroom door, disappearing into the crowded halls of students.\"\n\ntext: \"You follow in his tracks, gathering your belongings and meeting the crowd of students gathered in the corridor.\"\n\nnext:","x":-2350,"y":-5545,"width":385,"height":767,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"fd36f098a9531b40","type":"text","text":"# Creeper takes test bad mood\n\nenter: creeper\n\ntext: \"You pass your test forward to Professor Magnet, who begrudgingly yanks it from your grasp, nearly ripping the paper!\"\n\ntext: creeper(flustered): \"Thanks, [player_name], please return to your seat now.\"\n\nvar: test_score - 1\n\nnext: \\[\n{if: test_score > 7: \"Impossible Score\"}\n{if: test_score >= 6: \"Good Score\"}\n{if: test_score >= 4: \"Mid Score\"}\n{if: test_score > 0: \"Bad Score\"}\n{else: \"Bad Score\"}\n]","x":-5190,"y":-4341,"width":380,"height":562,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"8c8faf9f0de31c2a","type":"text","text":"# Creeper takes test good mood\n\nenter: creeper\n\ntext: \"You pass your test forward to Professor Magnet.\"\n\ntext: creeper(flustered): \"Thanks, [player_name]! Hoping you did excellent on the test.\"\n\nvar: test_score + 1\n\nnext: \\[\n{if: test_score > 8: \"Impossible Score\"}\n{if: test_score >= 6: \"Good Score\"}\n{if: test_score >= 3: \"Mid Score\"}\n{if: test_score > 0: \"Bad Score\"}\n{else: \"Bad Score\"}\n]","x":-5190,"y":-3700,"width":380,"height":541,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"aa66069bc6502a86","type":"text","text":"# Bad Score\n\nenter: creeper\n\ntext: \"After everyone has turned in their tests you watch Professor Magnet stand up from his desk and begin addressing the whole class.\"\n\ntext: creeper(flustered): \"It makes me sad to say this, but not everyone in this classroom passed today.\"\n\ntext: creeper(disappointed): \"In fact, a vast majority of you will not be returning to The Creeper's Campus tomorrow.\"\n\ntext: \"You hear gasps from many people around the room, including yourself.\"\n\ntext: creeper(idle): \"[player_name], would you please stand up. I truly thought you would be better than this.\"\n\ntext: creeper(flustered): \"In all of my years working as a professor I have yet to see a score as abysmal as yours...\"\n\ntext: creeper(disappointed): \"... In fact, I'm not even sure how you managed to score this low. It's astonishing and frankly even a little impressive.\"\n\ntext: creeper(idle): \"It is as if you *tried* to score this low. Which, admittedly, would be amusing, if it were not so pathetically sad. When you leave this school at the end of the day I do not want to see your face return here again.\"\n\ntext: \"Wow... You're completely lost. It's hard to think straight after what you just heard, coming from someone you've looked up to for so long? You feel nauseous...\"\n\nflag: end_on_first_day = true\n\nnext: \\[\n{if: seat = 1: \"Femchro Disgusted\"},\n{if: seat = 2: \"Lead Disgusted\"},\n{if: seat = 3: \"Flux Disgusted\"},\n{if: seat = 4: \"Primal Disgusted\"},\n{if: seat = 5: \"Ragno Disgusted\"},\n{if: seat = 6: \"Creeper Disgusted\"}\n]","x":-4730,"y":-4718,"width":380,"height":1300,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"48970726cb709b7d","type":"text","text":"# Good Score\n\nenter: creeper\n\ntext: \"After everyone has turned in their tests you watch Professor Magnet stand up from his desk and begin addressing the whole class.\"\n\ntext: creeper(flustered): \"It makes me sad to say this, but not everyone in this classroom passed today.\"\n\ntext: creeper(disappointed): \"In fact, a vast majority of you will not be returning to The Creeper's Campus tomorrow.\"\n\ntext: \"You hear gasps from many people around the room, including yourself.\"\n\ntext: \"Professor Magnet begins listing off the students who performed the best, making his way through list into the students who scored the lowest. You hear your own name early on.\"\n\ntext: creeper(flustered): \"Students who scored around 80%: [player_name].\"\n\ntext: \"You're not the only name called out during this portion of the Professor's reading, in fact most of the class is mentioned. You feel that the score isn't bad, but you could have done much better.\"\n\nnext: \\[\n{if: seat = 1: \"Femchro Congratulates\"},\n{if: seat = 2: \"Lead Congratulates\"},\n{if: seat = 3: \"Flux Congratulates\"},\n{if: seat = 4: \"Primal Congratulates\"},\n{if: seat = 5: \"Ragno Congratulates\"},\n{if: seat = 6: \"Creeper Congratulates\"}\n]","x":-4270,"y":-4458,"width":380,"height":1040,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"b03f1bdd98bde509","type":"text","text":"# End of Class\n\ntext: \"A million feet pitter patter across the floors of the hall as you attempt to push your way through the crowds. Eventually the hall opens into a larger room and the crowd parts into a ring.\"\n\nenter: nexus\n\ntext: \"In the middle of the student ring stands the Dean of The Creeper's College. You've never actually seen him before, but just by his dress and posture you know it's him.\"\n\ntext: \"He's just standing there... menacingly. Intently watching students passing back and forth, making it to their classes.\"\n\nexit: nexus\n\ntext: \"You continue on through the halls, if you wait any longer you're not going to have any time to eat!\"\n\nnext: \\[\n{if: forgot_lunchbox = false: \"Brought Lunchbox\"},\n{if: forgot_lunchbox = true: \"Forgot Lunchbox\"}\n{else: \"Brought Lunchbox\"}\n]","x":-1880,"y":-4150,"width":380,"height":779,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"541f5ce0fcb33274","type":"text","text":"# Creeper takes test\n\nnext: \\[\n{if: creeper_upset = false: \"Creeper takes test good mood\"},\n{else: \"Creeper takes test bad mood\"}\n]","x":-5650,"y":-3657,"width":380,"height":217,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"5f41bcc80d823d5e","type":"text","text":"# Test end\n\nnext: \\[\n{if: seat = 6: \"Creeper takes test\"},\n{else: \"Takes test self\"}\n]","x":-5650,"y":-3357,"width":380,"height":181,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"9577e8810d7ceefa","type":"text","text":"# Takes test self\n\ntext: \"You get up and take your test to the front of the class, placing it on Professor Magnet's desk. He doesn't bother to look up at you.\"\n\ntext: \"As you walk back to your seat it feels like the whole class is watching you... They're not though... right?\"\n\nnext: \\[\n{if: test_score > 7: \"Impossible Score\"}\n{if: test_score >= 6: \"Good Score\"}\n{if: test_score >= 4: \"Mid Score\"}\n{if: test_score > 0: \"Bad Score\"}\n{else: \"Bad Score\"}\n]","x":-5190,"y":-3079,"width":380,"height":500,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"a8f4d49864eb4945","type":"text","text":"# Impossible Score\n\nenter: creeper\n\ntext: \"After everyone has turned in their tests you watch Professor Magnet stand up from his desk and begin addressing the whole class.\"\n\ntext: creeper(flustered): \"It makes me sad to say this, but not everyone in this classroom passed today.\"\n\ntext: creeper(disappointed): \"In fact, a vast majority of you will not be returning to The Creeper's Campus tomorrow.\"\n\ntext: \"You hear gasps from many people around the room, including yourself.\"\n\ntext: creeper(idle): \"Before we get to that though, there is one person in this room who did outstandingly on the test! In fact, I'm unsure as to how they even managed to achieve this score.\"\n\ntext: creeper(flustered): \"[player_name], please stand up.\"\n\ntext: \"You get up from your seat, all eyes in the room are on you.\"\n\ntext: creeper(flustered): \"You scored the highest I have ever seen anyone score in all my years working as a professor—which admittedly are not many. Very impressive work!\"\n\ntext: \"Professor Magnet continues to read off test score, congratulating and belittling students as he goes. You're just happy you aced the test, and surprised you got so much praise!\"\n\nnext: \\[\n{if: seat = 1: \"Femchro Dumbfounded\"},\n{if: seat = 2: \"Lead Dumbfounded\"},\n{if: seat = 3: \"Flux Dumbfounded\"},\n{if: seat = 4: \"Primal Dumbfounded\"},\n{if: seat = 5: \"Ragno Dumbfounded\"},\n{if: seat = 6: \"Creeper Dumbfounded\"}\n]","x":-4727,"y":-3362,"width":380,"height":1224,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"d49d20fc0d170d36","type":"text","text":"# Mid Score\n\nenter: creeper\n\ntext: \"After everyone has turned in their tests you watch Professor Magnet stand up from his desk and begin addressing the whole class.\"\n\ntext: creeper(flustered): \"It makes me sad to say this, but not everyone in this classroom passed today.\"\n\ntext: creeper(disappointed): \"In fact, a vast majority of you will not be returning to The Creeper's Campus tomorrow.\"\n\ncharacter: creeper(idle)\n\ntext: \"You hear gasps from many people around the room, including yourself.\"\n\ntext: \"Professor Magnet begins listing off the students who performed the best, making his way through list into the students who scored the lowest. As he nears the end of the list you finally hear your name called.\"\n\ntext: creeper(flustered): \"For those who scored below 50%: [player_name]!\"\n\ntext: \"Despite not being the only name called the moment you hear it fall from the Professor's lips everything goes quiet... 50%? Really? You thought you knew data packs better than this... Maybe you're not cut out for this after all.\"\n\nnext: \\[\n{if: seat = 1: \"Femchro Consoles\"},\n{if: seat = 2: \"Lead Consoles\"},\n{if: seat = 3: \"Flux Consoles\"},\n{if: seat = 4: \"Primal Consoles\"},\n{if: seat = 5: \"Ragno Consoles\"},\n{if: seat = 6: \"Creeper Consoles\"}\n]","x":-4270,"y":-3362,"width":380,"height":1104,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"3d0253ca22baf92d","type":"text","text":"# Femchro Start Interaction\n\ntodo: Femchro sits in the seat right next to the player. They maintain their uppity-attitude.\n\nnext:","x":-8,"y":-4391,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"b8fb9a49516e310c","type":"text","text":"# Femchro Judges Food\n\ntodo: Femchro judges the player based on their choice of food.\n\nnext:","x":430,"y":-4391,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"d68bffed11ad820b","type":"text","text":"# Mystic Interrupts Femchro\n\ntodo: Mystic interrupts the player's interaction with Femchro. The player can choose to either stand up and fight back or forfeit their money to Mystic. Femchro judges the player accordingly.\n\nnext:","x":850,"y":-4391,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"aa57c1d73409297f","type":"text","text":"# Femchro End Interaction\n\ntodo: Closing remarks from Femchro as she leaves the cafeteria. The player follows out to the courtyard of the school.\n\nnext:","x":1270,"y":-4391,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"5b08521910475abd","type":"text","text":"# Ragno Start Interaction\n\ntodo: Ragno sits across from the player. They're looking to discuss the school and other characters.\n\nnext:","x":-8,"y":-4101,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"03bb140117c3dd18","type":"text","text":"# Ragno Judges Food\n\ntodo: Ragno judges the player based on their choice of food.\n\nnext:","x":430,"y":-4101,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"936bd6dd7b03796c","type":"text","text":"# Mystic Interrupts Ragno\n\ntodo: Mystic interrupts the player's interaction with Ragno. The player can choose to either stand up and fight back or forfeit their money to Mystic. Ragno judges the player accordingly.\n\nnext:","x":850,"y":-4101,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"3b5fa9a8beb8a706","type":"text","text":"# Ragno End Interaction\n\ntodo: Closing remarks from Ragno as they leave the cafeteria. The player follows out to the courtyard of the school.\n\nnext:","x":1270,"y":-4101,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"aaf04ae50d4ebed2","type":"text","text":"# Smithed Interrupts Femchro\n\ntodo: Mr. Smithed greets Femchro and the player, commenting on their relationship.\n\nnext:","x":-45,"y":-1723,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"44a6ad2fbe581c40","type":"text","text":"# Femchro End Remarks\n\ntodo: Femchro reacts differently based on various factors.\n\nnext:","x":435,"y":-1723,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"da5b79c56f86b37e","type":"text","text":"# Femchro Inquiry\n\ntodo: Femchro greets the player based on their previous interactions in the day, before being interrupted.\n\nnext:","x":-505,"y":-1723,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"ee7cfd99923f3e4b","type":"text","text":"# Ragno Inquiry\n\ntodo: Ragno greets the player based on their previous interactions in the day, before being interrupted.\n\nnext:","x":-505,"y":-1400,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"67b6215b1d7595eb","type":"text","text":"# Smithed Interrupts Ragno\n\ntodo: Mr. Smithed says that Ragno seems familiar, but can't quite place it. Comments on their relationship with the player.\n\nnext:","x":-45,"y":-1400,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"4a80fa47ad0993c2","type":"text","text":"# Ragno End Remarks\n\ntodo: Ragno reacts differently based on various factors.\n\nnext:","x":435,"y":-1400,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"3307914ff0897007","type":"text","text":"# Creeper Inquiry\n\ntodo: Creeper greets player based on their previous interactions in the day before being interrupted.\n\nnext:","x":-505,"y":-1097,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"6b1ba0f15abf9364","type":"text","text":"# Smithed Interrupts Creeper\n\ntodo: Mr. Smithed greets Magnet, questioning him on how the first day went for the new students. Questions player based on factors.\n\nnext:","x":-45,"y":-1097,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"e129aa73a5e2bdc6","type":"text","text":"# Creeper End Remarks\n\ntodo: Creeper reacts differently based on various factors.\n\nnext:","x":435,"y":-1097,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"2"}
	],
	"edges":[
